{"type": "article", "id": 2213, "title": "装饰艺术感包装的有机手工皂", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:41:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222254hoIvcVf5usq1RMS6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">英国人对手工香皂的偏爱你也许听说过。近日，东伦敦肥皂公司推出了一个有机手工肥皂品牌，融合了鳄梨、可可、橄榄油以及椰子油等可食用的物质，旨在打消人们对于化妆品成分的担忧与顾虑。该公司为了使其手工制作的特点得到放大，专门邀请包装设计公司为其设计了一个简洁图形与装饰艺术相结合的Art Deco 风格的黑白印花包装，极具现代感的同时，也让客户能够清晰感觉到这款手工香皂对于皮肤的无害性。定价 4 英镑，</span><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/LondonFieldsSoap\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134927Abv4LPHoh6JdZBgX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134928jGZ0rm7BqtVSFKD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.590625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134929WmELivCdhVGgRUOn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}